thread.title: Jill
thread.title_full: Ocean County Veterinary Hospital reviewed by Jill

author: Jill
title: Jill
text: I was satisfied with some things but I was very unhappy that the vet didn't even pet my dog or show him much attention at all. I'm not sure he even checked his teeth. I was concerned about a specific problem and it was just played down and I wasn't really listened to. The nurse that came in before the vet was more respectable then the vet. It was not a warm enviornment at all. And it was my dogs first vet experience. I was just hoping that it would of went a little better.
